# Review Helper

## Instructions

Review the patch carefully before it merges.

- Flag correctness, security, and maintainability risks.
- Keep findings prioritized and actionable.

## Source Notes

This skill was generated from the `skill-export-demo` shared agent. The source agent declares `read-only` sandbox expectations, but skill consumers must enforce permissions themselves.
